room_title: Escape room "Mars Outpost" by Sum Escape in Gambrills
room_description: With no response from the Mars research outpost, and the scheduled return date drawing near, you and your team have been tasked with a mission. Extract the scientists and all research data. Once on site, your team discovers the scientists are no where to be found. The incineration protocol fail-safe has been triggered and now you must find a way out before your time hits zero. Abort extraction mission, just get out while you can.
